.header-secound
  .header-secound__logo
    = link_to "#" do
      = image_tag "//www-mercari-jp.akamaized.net/assets/img/common/common/logo.svg?891577966", class: 'header-secound__logo__icon'
  .header-secound__signup-bar
    %ol.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--first
        会員情報
        .bubble.red-color
          %span.red-color
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--secound.red-color-text
        電話番号認証
        .bubble.red-color
          %span
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--third
        お届け先住所入力
        .bubble
          %span
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--forth
        支払い方法
        .bubble
          %span
      %li.header-secound__signup-bar__stepber--fifth
        完了
        .bubble
.main-secound
  .main-secound__block
    %h2.main-secound__block__title
      電話番号認証
  .main-secound__contents.bottom-space
    .main-secound__contents__container
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          認証番号
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__form
          %input.input-place{placeholder:"認証番号番を入力", type:"text"}
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__description
          SMSで届いた認証番号を入力してください
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__btn-next
          = link_to "認証して完了" ,"signup4" ,class:'link-white'
  .main-secound__contents.bottom-space
    .main-secound__contents__container
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text
          30秒たっても認証番号が届かない方へ
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__description
          電話で認証番号を聞くこともできます。
      .main-secound__contents__container__block  
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__btn-next
          = link_to "電話で認証番号を聞く（通話無料）" ,"signup4" ,class:'link-white'
  .main-secound__contents.bottom-space
    .main-secound__contents__container
      .main-secound__contents__container__block
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text{style: 'font-size:16px;'}
          認証番号を再送することもできます。もう一度電話番号を入力して下さい。
        .main-secound__contents__container__block__description
          = link_to "#" ,class:'link-return' do
            電話番号を再度入力する
        %p.main-secound__contents__container__block__text-message.small-text
          ※SMSが届かない場合は
          = link_to "SMS受信設定", "https://www.mercari.com/jp/tos_list/" ,class: 'link-blue'
          を確認して、もう一度電話番号を入力してください。
= render partial: 'footer'
